lines.textMessage: |Ohoho I didn't think the GREAT Cress would fall into my trap!
|Hey hold on a minute. I don't fall. I ran here.
|Like I said: I don't fall. I run all over you!
|Uh m'am? For an archeologist you seem pretty dumb.
|How am I the dumb one when you've decided to stand in my way?
|That's why I brought you some nice caffeine!
|You are a literal life saver Brozu. I'd kill for some coffee right now.
|Coffee... right. I'll just... leave this here and we'll see each other back at HQ. Later!
|Well so am I! Just thought I'd bring you a little support.
|...you mean coffee? You brought me coffee?
|Definitely. See ya later. Oh and remember my gift next time we duel!
|Oh, cool cool... keep doing that. I'll see you at the finish line.
|Not with that attitude it's not! See ya chump!
|BECAUSE OF ALL THESE NOISES SURROUNDING US
|Heh, nice one. Look I can turn into a lootbox.
|Oh, hello there little fella. Why aren't you attacking me?

|...wait. I remember you. You're one of the first Noises I caught! 
How... are you?
|Did you just say "Cat Noise"? I need to write this down this is incredible - wait don't go!
|That girl is driving me crazy. Whoa she dropped something... on purpose?
|You've been skipping on our training session!
|...no I haven't. Today is artifact day, remember?
|Don't give me excuses! Let me hear your battlecry!

name: A-Event> Fin VS Spark Dialogue Win #1

lines.textMessage: |You beat me... I've been a good teacher... now I can die in peace
|Spark proceeds to do a perfect backflip and then runs off.
|Hi! I don't know who you are or even where we are but I can see you're doing your best out here! I'll leave you a little gift to ease your struggle a bit. See ya!
|Ah I remember you. You're Cress' favorite right?
|Until she forgets them. Let's see if she'll remember you after I'm done here.
|You didn't! We got lost and now the leader of Azure Shield is going to kill us.
|Why does everyone think of me as a killer?
|Well.. are you standing in my way?
|Run back to your base and remember who gave you these bruises.
|I hope that didn't hurt TOO bad.
|You're just going to leave us here? There are Noises about!
|My agents will come and pick you up. We'll talk more at my HQ. See you there!
|Is your arm too heavy to use?
|Paper beats rock! \u2026Paper is made from trees, you see.
